OL,3,CPub bookings surge by 300% for
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup kick-off
OL,6,FPub bookings have surged by almost
OL,7,F300% as fans make plans to watch
OL,8,FEngland's World Cup kick-off, figures
OL,9,Fshow.
OL,11,FBookings for pub arrivals up to two
OL,12,Fhours before England's opener against
OL,13,FCroatia on Wednesday are up 293%
OL,14,Fcompared with the same date last year,
OL,15,Fwith hospitality set for 42% sales
OL,16,Fboost across the group stage,
OL,17,Faccording to technology provider Zonal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
