CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781686099
OL,3,CPub bookings surge by 300% for
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup kick-off
OL,6,FUKHospitality said the sector
OL,7,Fbenefited "enormously" from major
OL,8,Ffootball tournaments such as the World
OL,9,FCup.
OL,11,FEngland group games at Euro 2024
OL,12,Fdelivered a 42% sales increase,
OL,13,Ffigures showed, with UKHospitality
OL,14,Fpredicting a similar boost during this
OL,15,FWorld Cup.
OL,17,FKate Nicholls, chairwoman of
OL,18,FUKHospitality, said: "The pub is
OL,19,Fcategorically the best place to watch
OL,20,FEngland at the World Cup, both tonight
OL,21,Fand for the rest of the tournament.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@VO]zD@VOU
