OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781686099
OL,3,CPub bookings surge by 300% for
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup kick-off
OL,6,F"Bookings up almost 300% for tonight's
OL,7,Fgame shows that, despite the later
OL,8,Fthan usual kick-off times, England
OL,9,Ffans want to get together to watch the
OL,10,Fgame, cheer on the team and support
OL,11,Ftheir local.
OL,13,F"The World Cup will be a massive boost
OL,14,Ffor our pubs and bars, with sales set
OL,15,Fto be up more than 40% across the
OL,16,Fgroup stage as fans gather for the
OL,17,Fgames.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
