OL,3,CPub bookings surge by 300% for
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup kick-off
OL,6,F"Fingers crossed tonight's game is the
OL,7,Fstart of a long World Cup campaign for
OL,8,Fthe Three Lions, in what would be a
OL,9,Fhuge boost for both football fans and
OL,10,Fhospitality."
OL,12,FSeparate figures from polling firm
OL,13,FOpinium suggest 29% of UK adults are
OL,14,Fexpecting to watch World Cup matches
OL,15,Fin the pub, spending an extra #600
OL,16,Fmillion during the tournament alone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
